        "ai_content": "[TOOL_CALLS][{\"name\": \"tool_get_table_schema\", \"arguments\": {\"databaseName\": \"kvikkleire\", \"schemaName\": \"kvikkleire_87067f98e29a47d4901328f3a926a515\", \"table_name\": \"kvikkleirefaresoneavgr\"}, \"id\": \"Z6VY6VY6V\"}]\n\n**Plan**\n\n1. Get parcels in Trondheim municipality that intersect with quick-clay hazard areas with high risk class.\n2. Sort the parcels by `teigid` in ascending order.\n\n**Query**\n\n```sql\nSELECT k.teigid, k.teignavn, k.omrade, k.grense\nFROM kvikkleire.kartleggingsomrade AS k\nJOIN kvikkleire.kartleggingsomradekant AS kk ON ST_Intersects(k.omrade, kk.grense)\nJOIN kvikkleire.kvikkleirefaresoneavgr AS q ON ST_Intersects(k.omrade, q.grense)\nWHERE q.skredrisikokvikkleireklasse = 'H\u00f8y'\nAND k.kartleggingstatus = 'Godkjent'\nAND k.omrade @> (SELECT geometry FROM kommuner.municipality WHERE kommunenummer = '1501')\nLIMIT 10\n```\n\n**Validation**\n\n[{\"name\": \"tool_validate_sql\", \"arguments\": {\"sql\": \"SELECT k.teigid, k.teignavn, k.omrade, k.grense FROM kvikkleire.kartleggingsomrade AS k JOIN kvikkleire.kartleggingsomradekant AS kk ON ST_Intersects(k.omrade, kk.grense) JOIN kvikkleire.kvikkleirefaresoneavgr AS q ON ST_Intersects(k.omrade, q.grense) WHERE q.skredrisikokvikkleireklasse = 'H\u00f8y' AND k.kartleggingstatus = 'Godkjent' AND k.omrade @> (SELECT geometry FROM kommuner.municipality WHERE kommunenummer = '1501') LIMIT 10\", \"databaseName\": \"kvikkleire\", \"step_number\": 1}}]",
